==English==

===Phrase===
'''[[dumb]] [[blonde]]'''

# ''(pejorative):'' A female preoccupied with appearance while neglecting intellectual pursuits, (often taken to extremes.)
#:''Have you found the canonical list of '''dumb blonde''' jokes on the internet yet?''
# By extension, infrequently used to refer to blond males.

===Usage note===
Humor or otherwise, using the term to refer to a male will usually cause confusion.

